### How to Upload Manually (if needed)

1. Go to: https://github.com/davinspridgen-a11y/rythum/upload/main
2. Drag and drop `index.html` from this folder onto the upload zone
3. Add a commit message (e.g. "Update BitBeats UI redesign")
4. Click **Commit changes**

---

### Notes
- Claude is handling the upload automatically via browser injection.
- This file is a reference in case the automated upload needs to be retried.
- All other files (icons, MIDI, docs) live in this folder but only `index.html` is the active web app file that needs to be on GitHub.
